NOTE: The bundled `references/text_distillation/evidence_cards.jsonl` contains
text excerpts derived from 中医世家 (zysj.com.cn) public-domain classical
Chinese medical texts (伤寒论, 金匮要略, 本草纲目, etc.) for educational
and research purposes only. The data is not intended for clinical use
without verification by a licensed TCM practitioner.

These classical texts are in the public domain in China as their original
authors died more than 100 years ago. The excerpts are presented as
educational reference and should not be used as the sole basis for any
medical decision.
